# Full System Workflow — Complete Relationship & Communication Map
## Event Ticketing Platform — Phase 1A

---

## LAYER MAP OVERVIEW

```
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  EXTERNAL CLIENTS                                                    │
│   Next.js 14 (Browser)          Stripe (Webhook Caller)             │
│   k6 (Load Test Agent)          Stripe CLI (Local Dev Forwarder)    │
└─────────────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────┘
                                  │ HTTPS
┌─────────────────────────────────▼────────────────────────────────────┐
│  SECURITY LAYER  (Every request passes through this)                │
│   JwtFilter (OncePerRequestFilter)                                  │
│   CorrelationIdFilter (OncePerRequestFilter, Order=1)               │
│   Spring Security Filter Chain (SecurityConfig)                     │
│   @PreAuthorize on controller methods                               │
└─────────────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────┘
                                  │
┌─────────────────────────────────▼────────────────────────────────────┐
│  HTTP LAYER — Controllers (com.ticketing.{domain}.controller)        │
│   EventController          UserController                            │
│   BookingController        StripeWebhookController                  │
│   PaymentController        @ControllerAdvice (GlobalExceptionHandler)│
└──────────┬──────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────┘
           │                      │
           │ Service calls        │ @Transactional service call
           │ (no @Transactional   │ (PaymentService.handleStripeWebhook)
           │  on webhook ctrl)    │
┌──────────▼──────────────────────▼────────────────────────────────────┐
│  SERVICE LAYER — Business Logic (com.ticketing.{domain}.service)     │
│   EventService              @Transactional(readOnly = true) default  │
│   BookingService            write methods override @Transactional    │
│   PaymentService            @Retryable on reserveTickets()           │
│   InventoryService          @PostConstruct warm-up                  │
│   PricingEngineService      Strategy chain per booking               │
│   UserService               BCrypt password handling                 │
│   RefundService             3-tier refund policy                     │
│   WaitlistService                                                    │
│   BookingStateMachineService  factory.getStateMachine(bookingId)     │
│   DistributedLockService    Lua acquire + Lua release                │
└──────────┬──────────────────────┬──────────────────────┬─────────────┘
           │                      │                      │
    DB calls               Redis calls           RabbitMQ publishes
           │                      │                      │
┌──────────▼──────────┐  ┌────────▼────────┐   ┌────────▼────────────┐
│  DATA LAYER         │  │  REDIS 7        │   │  RABBITMQ 3.12      │
│  JPA Repositories   │  │  Inventory      │   │  booking.exchange   │
│  Hibernate ORM      │  │  counters       │   │  notification.exch  │
│  HikariCP pool      │  │  Distributed    │   │  Queues + DLQs      │
│  TIMESTAMPTZ        │  │  lock tokens    │   │  Dead Letter Queues │
│  ENUM types         │  │  Event cache    │   └────────┬────────────┘
│  @Version optim.lk  │  │  Lua scripts    │            │
│  soft delete        │  │  @Cacheable     │   ┌────────▼────────────┐
│  partial indexes    │  └─────────────────┘   │  ASYNC LISTENERS   │
│  Flyway migrations  │                        │  NotificationLstnr  │
└──────────┬──────────┘                        │  QRCodeGenLstnr     │
           │                                   │  WaitlistLstnr      │
┌──────────▼──────────┐                        └────────┬────────────┘
│  POSTGRESQL 15      │                                 │
│  9 tables           │◄────────────────────────────────┘
│  V1–V9 Flyway       │  (listeners may write back to DB)
│  ACID guarantees    │
│  Source of truth    │
└─────────────────────┘
```

