## FLOW 1 — User Registration & Login

```
Browser                Spring Boot               PostgreSQL
  │                         │                        │
  ├─POST /api/auth/register─►│                        │
  │                         ├─validate DTO (@Valid)   │
  │                         ├─BCrypt.encode(password) │
  │                         ├─userRepo.save(user)────►│
  │                         │                        ├─INSERT users
  │                         │                        │  role=USER (ENUM)
  │◄─201 {userId, email}────┤◄───────────────────────┤
  │                         │                        │
  ├─POST /api/auth/login────►│                        │
  │  {email, password}      ├─userRepo.findByEmail()─►│
  │                         │◄────────────User entity─┤
  │                         ├─BCrypt.matches(raw,hash)│
  │                         ├─JwtService.generateToken│
  │◄─200 {jwt, expiresIn}───┤                        │
```

**Cross-cutting:** `CorrelationIdFilter` adds `X-Correlation-ID` to MDC before any of these steps. Every log line from `UserService` includes the correlation ID automatically.

---

## FLOW 2 — Event Browsing (Read Path with Cache)

```
Browser          JwtFilter       EventController    EventService      Redis     PostgreSQL
  │                  │                │                  │               │           │
  ├─GET /api/events──►│               │                  │               │           │
  │  JWT optional    ├─(skip if pub)  │                  │               │           │
  │                  ├──────────────►│                  │               │           │
  │                  │              ├─eventSvc.getEvents()               │           │
  │                  │              │                  ├─@Cacheable hit?─►│          │
  │                  │              │                  │               ├─HIT: return│
  │                  │              │                           MISS:  │           │
  │                  │              │                  ├──────────────────────────►│
  │                  │              │                  │  @EntityGraph JOIN FETCH   │
  │                  │              │                  │  (event + category + venue)│
  │                  │              │                  │◄──────Page<Event>──────────┤
  │                  │              │                  ├─map to EventResponse DTOs  │
  │                  │              │                  ├─store in Redis cache        │
  │◄─200 Page<Event>─┤──────────────┤◄─────────────────┤               │           │
```

**Optimization path:** Second browser request within 10 minutes hits Redis, never touches PostgreSQL. `@Transactional(readOnly = true)` skips Hibernate dirty checking. Composite index `idx_events_status_date` used for filtered queries.

