## STATE MACHINE — Complete State Transition Map

```
                    ┌─────────────┐
                    │  AVAILABLE  │ ← tier has seats
                    └──────┬──────┘
                           │ ADD_TO_CART
                           │ guard: SeatsAvailableGuard
                           │ action: StartReservationTimerAction
                    ┌──────▼──────┐
                    │  RESERVED   │ ← 5-min window
                    └──────┬──────┘
           ┌───────── ─────┤
           │               │ PROCEED_TO_CHECKOUT
           │ TIMER_EXPIRED │
           │ action:       │
           │ ReleaseSeats  ▼
           │        ┌─────────────────┐
           │        │ PAYMENT_PENDING │ ← Stripe session created
           │        └──────┬──────────┘
           ▼               │ PAYMENT_SUCCESS          │ PAYMENT_FAILURE
    ┌──────────┐           │ action: ConfirmBooking   │ action: ReleaseSeats
    │ EXPIRED  │           │ action: GenerateQRCode   ▼
    └──────────┘    ┌──────▼──────┐           ┌──────────────┐
                    │  CONFIRMED  │           │ PAYMENT_FAILED│
                    └──────┬──────┘           └──────────────┘
                           │
           ┌───────────────┼────────────────┐
           │ REQUEST_REFUND│ CHECK_IN        │ EVENT_CANCELLED
           │               │ guard:CheckIn   │ action: CancelBooking
           ▼               │ guard          │ action: StripeFullRefund
    ┌──────────────┐       ▼                ▼
    │REFUND_REQUEST│  ┌──────────┐    ┌───────────┐
    └──────┬───────┘  │ ATTENDED │    │ CANCELLED │
           │          └──────────┘    └───────────┘
    ┌──────┴──────┐
    │             │ DENY_REFUND
    │ APPROVE_    │ action: NotifyRefundDenied
    │ REFUND      ▼
    │      ┌──────────────┐
    │      │ REFUND_DENIED│  ← stores refundDenialReason
    ▼      └──────────────┘
┌──────────────┐
│REFUND_APPROVED│  ← Stripe refund issued
└──────────────┘
```

**Terminal states** (no outgoing transitions): `ATTENDED`, `EXPIRED`, `PAYMENT_FAILED`, `REFUND_APPROVED`, `REFUND_DENIED`, `CANCELLED`

**EVENT_CANCELLED** can reach `CANCELLED` from `CONFIRMED`, `RESERVED`, and `PAYMENT_PENDING` — three source states, one target.
